column5: Hi gang,  I have combined both my passions or hobbies if you will, of fishing and songwriting/recording. Nothing serious here when it comes to fishing or the songwriting stuff as it's all just for the fun of it. I got a Go Pro in the spring and I've been filming all of my fishing adventures since then. I also wrote and recorded some original fishing songs to accompany my videos. I figure that I probably have enough footage to make 4-5 videos.  Check it out, I hope you enjoy!  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nn3D0d4Jz-k
Awesome job, that song is going to be stuck in my head all day!
Nice video thanks for sharing.  Art
Nice video thanks for sharing.  Art  x2
Tons of amazing footage there, wow...Love the float tube brookies especially, are you trout fishing in On or Qc?
That gets a blown out, 10 out of 10.  Enjoyed.  Thanks for taking the time.
Not so bad watching the screen . Good job    ...
I did, that was cool, that song gets in your head

Thanks for the kind comments everyone!   Tons of amazing footage there, wow...Love the float tube brookies especially, are you trout fishing in On or Qc?  To me living in Ottawa means enjoying the fishing opportunities on both sides of the Ottawa river. Some of those brookies in the video were caught in Ontario and some were caught in Quebec.
